          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "If one reduces the measurements of R.L.Macklin and",
                "J.H. Gibbons, J,NSE,31,343,1968 by a factor of 10,",
                "their values above ~5 MeV are only slightly below the",
                "present results and are within the sum of the stated",
                "errors. However, in going from 5 to 4.5 MeV, the",
                "earlier values decrease to ~50% of the present data",
                "and remain at about this level to the lowest",
                "alpha-particle energies. We conclude that the earlier",
                "thick-target yields are in error and should be",
                "replaced by the present data. (Author)"
              ]
            }
          ],
